<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-08-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-08-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="5" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d5">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72111/88½</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">President <gloss type="from">Wilson</gloss> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-17">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 17, 1914</hi>.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Secretary</hi>: I am returning the
                            enclosed papers<note n="10" xml:id="d5fn1">See Mr. Lansing’s memorandum
                                of Aug. 7, 1914, <ref target="#pg_1">p. 1</ref>, and his letter of
                                Aug. 14, 1914, to the Secretary of State, <ref target="#pg_3">p.
                                    3</ref>.</note> because it is evidently too late to pursue the
                            course suggested by them. Things have developed very fast in the East
                            since you were kind enough to submit them to me.</p>
                        <p>Cordially and faithfully yours,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodrow Wilson</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>